application.model

Class OnlineCatalog

  • java.lang.Object
    • application.model.OnlineCatalog

  • public class OnlineCatalog
extends Object
    Class which maintains the STIG data displayed and accessed from the Online Catalog scene. Shows the full Online Catalog and allows the user to download specified STIG XML files.

      • loadOnlineCatalog

        public void loadOnlineCatalog(javafx.scene.control.ListView<String> onlineCatalogList)
                       throws IOException
        Loads the list of available STIGs and displays them in the Online Catalog List. Called from initialize method.
        Parameters:
        onlineCatalogList - Passes the ListView object to display all STIGs.
        Throws:
        IOException - when there is an error reading the STIG list

      • queueFiles

        public void queueFiles(javafx.scene.control.ListView<String> filestbd)
        Adds the specified files from "Online Catalog" List to "Files to be Downloaded" list. Used with the right arrow button
        Parameters:
        filestbd - the list of files to be downloaded

      • downloadFiles

        public void downloadFiles(javafx.scene.control.ListView<String> filestbd)
                   throws IOException
        Finds and stores the specified XML file links, then downloads each specified XML file within the "Files to be Downloaded" list. Used with the "Download" button Clears the "Files to be Downloaded" list once downloading finishes.
        Parameters:
        filestbd - Passes ListView Object to create XML links from.
        Throws:
        IOException - when there is an issue with downloading the file
